                This assessment consists of <strong>5 Sorting Games</strong>.<br>
                For each game, 10 items will appear. You must categorize them correctly.<br>
                Your progress is tracked automatically.
            </p>
            <br>
            <button class="start-btn" onclick="changeLevel('0'); document.getElementById('level-select').value='0'">Start Level 1</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Universal Game Arena -->
    <div id="game-arena" class="game-container hidden">
        <div>
            <h2 id="level-title">Level Title</h2>
